#

Pork Carnitas Tacos with Pineapple Salsa and Avocado Crema

$15.99
800 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

MexicanComfort FoodStreet Food

Description

Savory, tender pork wrapped in soft tortillas, topped with zesty pineapple salsa and creamy avocado.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 3 lbs
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Cumin: 2 tsp
  • Oregano: 1 tsp
  • Black pepper: 1 tsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Lime juice: 1/4 cup
  • Corn tortillas: 12
  • Pineapple: 1 cup, diced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Avocado: 2, ripe
  • Sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Jalapeño: 1, minced
